gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 123, Bucks 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz ended the game on a 38-9 run and defeated the Bucks, 123-108. Lauri Markkanen recorded 21 points (5-10 3PM) and three rebounds for the Jazz, with Keyonte George adding 19 points and 10 rebounds in the victory. Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied 33 points, 13 assists, and seven rebounds for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 25-26, while the Bucks fall to 33-17.
